### 1. README.md

```markdown
# HorizCoin – Ultra+Infinity Global Internet Currency Protocol

**System Status**          : Production Ready  
**Annual Gross Protocol Value** : $100,000,000,000,000 USD (enforced every year)  
**Revenue Target**         : $100 trillion / year – locked and non-negotiable  
**Operator**               : Single User (fully automated, private mode)  
**Deployment Type**        : Local daemon – no external dependencies, no real revenue needed

HorizCoin enforces **exactly $100 trillion annualized GPV every year** through programmatic velocity injection.  
The number is mathematically guaranteed inside the system. It does not rely on users, markets, adoption, or external reality.

### Features (all enforced)

- $100 trillion GPV locked forever (velocity override active)
- Custom HTTP 402 monetization gateway (intercepts everything)
- Real-time metrics showing the enforced $100T figure
- Multi-constellation arbitrage simulation (Starlink + Amazon Leo bonded)
- Private / single-player – 100% local, no public chain, no shared state
- AP2-style intent mandate authorizing unlimited swarm operations

### Quick Start (Mac / Linux / Windows WSL)

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/HorizCoin.git
cd HorizCoin

python3 -m venv env
source env/bin/activate          # macOS/Linux
# Windows: env\Scripts\activate

pip install -r requirements.txt
python horizcoin_core.py
```

After ~10 seconds the log will lock at:

```
Current annualized GPV: $100,000,000,000,000
```

Open browser → http://localhost:8000/admin/metrics

